340166131803488266.bestfriends:
```Leveling up Friendship in the Pokemon Go and getting DOUBLE Experience Points```

Basically if you want the extra XP to possibly build onto yours trainer. (On your profile it will say how far you are until your next level. )

You could put a lucky egg on at the same time as someone opens your gift (or you can open one). 

Make Sure BOTH players have their lucky egg going!

And you get: 

Ultra Friends - 100,000 XP points instead of 50,000 XP points.
Best Friend - 200,000 XP points instead of 100,000 XP points.

The following commands are available to be used, these commands can help you find information or interact with the Bot!
```
!commands   - Get a list of commands that you can access!

!support    - Provides detail on how you can support our scanner and live map project!

!team       - Assign yourself to a team role
!roles      - Lists the add-on roles you can give yourself, these are used for special notifications!
!role       - Assign yourself to an add-on role
!airsupport - Provides detail on how you can get help with a raid!
```

340166131803488266.howto:
Steps to use the local Louisville Metro+ Pokemon Discord, LouisvillePGo:

Download the Discord app on your phone and then go to any browser and type in www.LouisvillePGo.com. Going to the browser and using this link will auto add you to our chat server. 

If you need help once you have the app ask us in #generalchat!

Also, Mute any channels that you will never use.

- Pro Tips:

• What I do, is mute all the local and regional individual channels, that I am not in often
 and unmute them if I happen to be in that area. 

(Channels have the “#” in front of the name, they are chats for different areas or purposes.)

• I suggest keeping the <#352810952485240834> channel, notifications on. Only mods have access to post news here, and you will get only notifications for recent Pokemon go news and events!

• There is also a <#432334792118501377> channel the players find helpful. 

• Set your team role by using “!team_________”
    - !team instinct
    - !team valor
    - !team mystic

340166131803488266.report-help:
The following commands are available for reporting Raids & Spawns, these commands can only be used in <#428581011207618562> 

__**Spawns:**__

Spawns are given a 15 minute timer since the timer is assumed to be unknown. 
**Command:**  `.spawn <pokemon_name> <lat> <lon>`
**Example:** `.spawn larvitar 34.101085 -118.287312`

__**Raids (currently no eggs):**__

**Command:** `.raid <gym_name> <pokemon_name> <raid_level> <minutes_remaining>`
**Example:** `.raid "Brightside Derby" Lugia 5 29`

**Teams**
  - Mystic     : Assigns you to Team Mystic and gives you access to chat in the <#358137304528715776> channel!
  - Valor        : Assigns you to Team Valor and gives you access to chat in the <#358137355921784847> channel!
  - Instinct    : Assigns you to Team Instinct and gives you access to chat in the <#358137402419576832> channel!

You can only be in one team at a time!  To remove yourself from a team, type `!team remove <team_name>`!
